T1  - Community isomorphism and corporate social action
AU  - Marquis, Christopher
AU  - Glynn, Mary Ann
AU  - Davis, Gerald F.
Y1  - 2007/07/01
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.2007.25275683
